2.5 (2022-06-28)
- Change directory to comploy on execution, making it possible to execute it
from wherever

2.4 (2022-03-30)
- On deployment, Composer now makes sure that the autoloader is optimized and that dev-packages are left out
- It is now possible to execute custom serverside commands after deployment

2.3 (2022-03-12)
- rsync now uses the `--delay-updates` option to ensure better atomicity on deployment server.

2.2 (2022-03-11)
- Composer now uses the `--optimize-autoloader` option when installing packages on the server.

2.1 (2022-03-11)
- Ignore .git folder if using git.

2.0 (2022-03-10)
- First documented version.
- Added support for Composer, comploy now auto-installs packages on execution.
- Fixed bash conditionals.
- Now uses the deployment folder for permission setup.
